data.revised_prompt: A captivating image showcasing a professionally photographed Orange Glazed Chicken. The dish captures the essence of gourmet cuisine, with caramelized orange glaze perfectly coating a well-cooked chicken that's golden-brown in color. The chicken is beautifully presented on a porcelain white plate, garnished with fresh herbs. In the background, there's a soft blur to enhance the focus on the dish, with subtle suggestions of a rustic wooden table and soft, warm lighting glowing onto the plate from above, illuminating each detail of the culinary delight.
